sentences: Mai Hoshimura (星村 麻衣, Hoshimura Mai, born April 18, 1981 in Matsue, Shimane) is a Japanese pop singer-songwriter and pianist.
On May 31, 2009, her contract with Sony ended.
Mai Hoshimura was born on April 18, 1981 in Matsue, Shimane.
Her 2007 song "Sakura Biyori" was the tenth ending theme of the anime Bleach.
